.Dd July 25, 2025
.Dt DHCPSD_LEASEFILE 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm leasefile
.Nd persitent storage for allocated leases
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
will save allocated leases to persistent storage so they can be re-loaded
when the DHCP server restarts.
.Pp
.Nm
records the IP address, leased time, expiry time, flags and Client ID in
.Pa @DBDIR@/dhcp.leases
which is a tab separated text file.
This file is saved when
.Nm dhcpsd
exits and every
.Sy 30
seconds when it is running if there is something to save.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr dhcpsd 8 ,
.Xr dhcpsd_auto 8 .
